You are here: Get Started Using Einstein Discovery

Start here if you are new to Einstein Discovery.

Einstein Discovery augments your business intelligence with statistical modeling and machine learning to identify, surface, and visualize insights into your business data. It's integrated into your Salesforce environment so that you can quickly operationalize data analysis, predictions, and improvements with clicks, not code.

Jumpstart Solutions with Model Templates
Model templates provide out-of-the-box solution starter kits that you can customize to your solution requirements. They provide end-to-end implementations of common business use cases designed to integrate seamlessly with your Salesforce data.

Ethical AI in Einstein Discovery
Einstein Discovery offers bias detection and model cards to help you practice ethical use of artificial intelligence (AI) in your business.

Einstein Discovery Capacities and Requirements
Einstein Discovery has limits for CRM Analytics datasets, models, and predictions.

View Usage Statistics for Einstein Discovery
Einstein Discovery monitors usage statistics in real time. You can view the usage statistics in your org.
